title: Youtube sizes messed up
content:
This started almost a month ago at this point. I had been using Picture in Picture for a while and then I went to watch a new video and noticed the size was messed up.

Default view, the first picture is much larger and if there's anything on the side of the video like playlists, chat or recommended vids, the video will play under it

Theater mode has the video be pretty much the right size

Full screen is pretty much the default view but the rest is black

Sometimes if I wait a while and go back to the tab it'll be fixed but refreshing or changing the size starts it up again.

Did I break something? How do I fix this?

title: Mozilla browser Error message when printing file from Google cloud
content: Getting "Mozilla Firefox Crash Reporter" problem message when attempting to print files (Docs & Sheets) from Google Cloud. Errors messages have appeared on Lenova Thinkpad laptop in Firefox since mid Dec update. Can print existing files located on desktop, just not from cloud. Both HP and Epson Printers test fine, can print 'test pages'. Tried downloading files from cloud to pc....opening downloads, got same Firefox problem message and crashed. Have used same firefox browser and same printers for several years. Rebooted several times, same error. Can print, 'printer test pages'. Do I have a switch turned off/on or is this a browser problem. Any assistance would be appreciated.
creator: ggerlinger

title: erreur 403 sur site googlegroup
content:
bonjour

Je suis administrateur d'un Google Workspace, et depuis la dernière mise à jour de Firefox, lorsque j'essaye de me connecter à la page des paramètres avancés d'un groupe Google, Google me renvoie Erreur 403. Avant la mise à jour, cela fonctionnait parfaitement. Si je passe par un autre navigateur, par exemple Edge, je n'ai pas de message d'erreur et j'arrive à me connecter.

J'ai bien la dernière version à jour de Firefox (146.0.1)

Pouvez vous m'aider ?

Merci
